OL,3,CEmbattled fire boss quits in social
OL,4,Cmedia post alleging threats and
OL,5,Cdishonesty
OL,7,FOliver Lee, the suspended interim
OL,8,Fchief executive of West Midlands Fire
OL,9,FService (WMFS), has resigned in a
OL,10,Fdramatic social media post, claiming
OL,11,Fhe was threatened and pressured to
OL,12,Fremain silent on critical governance
OL,13,Fissues within the organisation.
OL,15,FLee, a former Royal Marine colonel,
OL,16,Fannounced his decision, citing ongoing
OL,17,Fthreats, including a High Court
OL,18,Finjunction, as well as personal
OL,19,Fconcerns about the integrity of WMFS
OL,20,Fleadership.
