OL,7,FLee described it as "another post
OL,8,Foffice" referring to the scandal over
OL,9,Fthe mistreatment of Postmasters.
OL,11,F"I have been threatened repeatedly,
OL,12,Fmainly to stay quiet on vital subjects
OL,13,Fin the public interest," Lee wrote.
OL,15,F"I will not be gagged. Nor will I
OL,16,Fdestroy my family with vast legal
OL,17,Fbills. I have therefore resigned in
OL,18,Forder to do what is right."
