OL,7,FLee's resignation follows a tumultuous
OL,8,Fperiod for the fire service, which
OL,9,Fsuspended him earlier in the week
OL,10,Fpending an investigation into
OL,11,Fgovernance concerns.
OL,13,FIn his post, Lee accused the
OL,14,Fleadership, specifically Fire
OL,15,FAuthority Chair Cllr Greg Brackenridge
OL,16,Fand Monitoring Officer Satinder
OL,17,FSahota, of dishonesty, contributing to
OL,18,Fwhat he described as a toxic
OL,19,Fenvironment within the service.
