OL,7,F"The chair of the Fire Authority, Greg
OL,8,FBrackenridge, is untruthful," Lee
OL,9,Fclaimed, going on to allege that
OL,10,FBrackenridge misrepresented his
OL,11,Fmilitary service.
OL,13,F"Neither (Brackenridge nor Sahota)
OL,14,Ftells the truth, hence the malaise at
OL,15,FWest Midlands Fire Service."
OL,17,FLee's resignation comes just days
OL,18,Fafter the Fire Authority suspended
OL,19,Fhim, citing allegations of potentially
OL,20,Funlawful actions linked to his
OL,21,Fsuspension of a senior finance officer.
