OL,7,FAccording to the authority's legal
OL,8,Fteam, a Section 5 report was issued,
OL,9,Faccusing Lee of maladministration.
OL,11,FThe suspension was to be ratified by
OL,12,Fthe full Fire Authority on 14th
OL,13,FOctober, with an independent
OL,14,Finvestigation into Lee's conduct
OL,15,Fexpected to follow.
OL,17,FIn a statement earlier this week,
OL,18,FBrackenridge expressed regret over the
OL,19,Fdecision to suspend Lee, calling it
OL,20,F"hugely deflating" and acknowledging
OL,21,Fthe public concern it would raise.
