OL,7,FLee's departure adds another layer of
OL,8,Funcertainty to what has already been a
OL,9,Fdifficult year for West Midlands Fire
OL,10,FService.
OL,12,FIn his post, Lee lamented that the
OL,13,Forganisation, which employs around
OL,14,F1,900 staff, remains "scared, cowed
OL,15,Fand not able to be itself," and
OL,16,Fsuggested that the service's problems
OL,17,Fare systemic.
