OL,7,F"West Midlands Fire Service will now
OL,8,Fsadly continue as was when I inherited
OL,9,Fit: scared, cowed, and not able to be
OL,10,Fitself. Viewing its leaders as
OL,11,Fselfish."
OL,13,FThe day-to-day running of the service
OL,14,Fwill now be overseen by Deputy Chief
OL,15,FFire Officer Simon Barry and the
OL,16,Fremaining leadership team, who have
OL,17,Fbeen tasked with maintaining
OL,18,Foperations while the governance issues
OL,19,Fcontinue to be investigated.
